com.mostc.pftt.results
Class PhpUnitResultWriter

java.lang.Object
  com.mostc.pftt.results.AbstractTestResultRW
      com.mostc.pftt.results.AbstractPhpUnitRW
          com.mostc.pftt.results.PhpUnitResultWriter

@NotThreadSafe
public class PhpUnitResultWriter
extends AbstractPhpUnitRW

Writes PhpUnitTestResults from a single test run with a single scenario set on a single host with a single build. Roughly follows the JUnit-like log file that `phpunit -log-junit` produces. Modified to: -write each result during the test run (otherwise, if pftt or phpunit crashed during test run, all results would be lost) -tally results using PFTT's modified statuses for PHPUnit

Author:
Matt Ficken
See Also:
EPhpUnitTestStatus, PhpUnitTestResult
